code: @InvokeOnHeader(ConsulEventActions.FIRE) protected void fire(Message message) throws Exception {     setBodyAndResult(message, getClient().fireEvent(getMandatoryHeader(message, ConsulConstants.CONSUL_KEY, getConfiguration().getKey(), String.class), message.getHeader(ConsulConstants.CONSUL_OPTIONS, EventOptions.BLANK, EventOptions.class), message.getBody(String.class))). }

@InvokeOnHeader(ConsulEventActions.LIST) protected void list(Message message) throws Exception {     setBodyAndResult(message, getClient().listEvents(message.getHeader(ConsulConstants.CONSUL_KEY, getConfiguration().getKey(), String.class), message.getHeader(ConsulConstants.CONSUL_OPTIONS, QueryOptions.BLANK, QueryOptions.class))). }
